@startuml
' Diagram: F05 - Thanh toan goi tra phi va cho duyet (Sequence)
' Status: WIP
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD adb1a28
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/SubscriptionPage.xaml.cs: OnMuaGoiClicked()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/PaymentPage.xaml.cs: SetupUi(), OnDaChuyenKhoanClicked()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/DeviceIdentity.cs: GetDeviceId()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/ApiConnectionPrompt.cs: EnsureConnectedApiBaseUrlAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/PaymentStatusPage.xaml.cs: StartPollingAsync(), PollStatusAsync(), ClosePaymentFlowAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/SubscriptionController.cs: CreateRequest(), GetRequestStatus()
' Note: Sequence da bo Preferences.GetDeviceId() vi code hien dung DeviceIdentity.GetDeviceId().
title F05 - Thanh toan goi tra phi va cho duyet

actor Guest
participant SubscriptionPage
participant PaymentPage
participant PaymentStatusPage
participant MainPage
participant DeviceIdentity
participant Preferences
participant ApiConnectionPrompt
participant AppConfig
participant "SubscriptionController" as SubscriptionController
participant "VietQR / Ngan hang" as Bank
database DB

Guest -> SubscriptionPage: chon goi tra phi
SubscriptionPage -> PaymentPage: PushModalAsync(loaiGoi)
PaymentPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
DeviceIdentity -> Preferences: doc override/device_id\nhoac tao stable id
DeviceIdentity --> PaymentPage: deviceId
PaymentPage -> PaymentPage: SetupUi()\n_tao noi dung chuyen + QR URL
PaymentPage -> Bank: hien QR / thong tin chuyen khoan

Guest -> PaymentPage: bam "Da chuyen khoan"
PaymentPage -> ApiConnectionPrompt: EnsureConnectedApiBaseUrlAsync(this, http)
ApiConnectionPrompt -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
AppConfig --> ApiConnectionPrompt: apiBaseUrl?
alt ket noi API thanh cong
  ApiConnectionPrompt --> PaymentPage: apiBaseUrl
  PaymentPage -> SubscriptionController: POST /api/subscription/request
  SubscriptionController -> DB: insert YeuCauThanhToan(TrangThai="cho_duyet")
  DB --> SubscriptionController: YeuCauId
  SubscriptionController --> PaymentPage: 200 OK (YeuCauId)
  PaymentPage -> PaymentStatusPage: PushModalAsync(yeuCauId,...)

loop moi 10 giay cho den khi co ket qua
  PaymentStatusPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
  PaymentStatusPage -> SubscriptionController: GET /api/subscription/request/{yeuCauId}
  SubscriptionController -> DB: doc YeuCauThanhToan\nneu da_duyet thi tim DangKyApp con han
  DB --> SubscriptionController: trangThai + ngayHetHan?
  SubscriptionController --> PaymentStatusPage: JSON trang thai

  alt da_duyet
    PaymentStatusPage -> Preferences: Set(sub_ngay_het_han)
    PaymentStatusPage -> Guest: hien ViewDaDuyet
    Guest -> PaymentStatusPage: OnBatDauClicked()
    PaymentStatusPage -> PaymentStatusPage: ClosePaymentFlowAsync(true)
    PaymentStatusPage -> MainPage: PushAsync(new MainPage) neu can\nRemovePage(SubscriptionPage)
    PaymentStatusPage -> PaymentStatusPage: loop dung do _pollCts da Cancel()
  else tu_choi
    PaymentStatusPage -> Guest: hien ViewTuChoi + ly do
    Guest -> PaymentStatusPage: OnThuLaiClicked()/OnDongClicked()
    PaymentStatusPage -> PaymentStatusPage: PopModalAsync()\nhoac ClosePaymentFlowAsync(false)
    PaymentStatusPage -> PaymentStatusPage: loop dung do _pollCts da Cancel()
  else cho_duyet
    PaymentStatusPage -> PaymentStatusPage: cap nhat countdown 10s
  end
end
else khong tim thay API dung
  ApiConnectionPrompt --> PaymentPage: null
  PaymentPage -> Guest: hien loi ket noi
end
@enduml
